List Available Algorithms

Source: R/obwoe.R
obwoe_algorithms.Rd

Returns a data frame with all available binning algorithms.

Usage

obwoe_algorithms()

Value

A data frame with algorithm information.

Examples

obwoe_algorithms()
#>    algorithm numerical categorical multinomial
